|`ResourceUsage`|<span data-ttu-id="9ff4f-450">Especifica el consumo de CPU del reconocedor.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ff4f-450">Specifies the recognizer's CPU consumption.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9ff4f-451">El intervalo es de 0 a 100.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ff4f-451">The range is from 0 to 100.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="9ff4f-452">El valor predeterminado es 50.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="9ff4f-452">The default value is 50.</span></span>|  
